{"tid":1916364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再次宣布  武肺大機會成功傳比狗隻","createTime":"2020-03-08T22:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T02:29:42.000Z","uid":134033,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"891f958198aa5df14d90cad8b5e2fd36e613f9c4","tid":1916364,"uid":134033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T22:18:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Sorry 我指既唔係成年狗隻</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而係幼犬</span><br />\n<br />\n不詳述  大家集氣等好消息<br />\n<br />\n用盡一切手段都要班狗落地獄<br />\n<br />\n而呢個方法  我地都猶豫左一段時間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過細路仔發病應該會快d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道自己支持到幾耐<br />\n<br />\n可能好快就消失  逐漸被遺忘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位手足  肯敢於犧牲  <br />\n<br />\n改變到香港既  <br />\n<br />\n可能只係一隻奶滿口水漬既右手 <br />\n<br />\n一張咳到有彩色痰  新鮮既紙巾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n超市入面  一番近距離 自言自語<br />\n<br />\n無心搭嗲  支持警察既言論<br />\n<br />\n而呢班傻閪狗仔女  父母 <br />\n<br />\n係有機會唔帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被捉到既機會係極低   防不勝防<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三萬隻狗  咁多隻母狗 狗仔女<br />\n<br />\n佢地有可能防得哂咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地行出左無人性既一步<br />\n<br />\n傻閪政府係捉唔哂潛在感染者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位  唔知係咪感染左  <br />\n<br />\n又或者  小小感冒既手足<br />\n<br />\n都可以從自己身邊既狗隻朋友 藍絲落手<br />\n<br />\n革命就係戰爭  血係必須要流"},{"pid":"c3f49945b434d685d128938839d1ab37a481b725","tid":1916364,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T23:43:11.000Z","msg":"集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad9a9e8312bd19eed38916d741bb95a83b58c05","tid":1916364,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T23:44:11.000Z","msg":"辛苦手足了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"